{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"bd4500dda8","title":"郵城战役结束后应向西进击","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c4ca254549","index":0,"year":1946,"month":11,"day":1,"articleId":"bd4500dda8"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji22","name":"毛泽东全集第22卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji22.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji22":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d167d024c7","type":"paragraph","text":"邮城战役结束后应向西进击！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"bd4500dda8"},{"id":"194fc3cbf4","type":"paragraph","text":"（1946年11月1日）刘、邓：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"bd4500dda8"},{"id":"391460b796","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）歼灭刘汝明尚郸城进攻四个团中之两个团，甚好甚感希望你们继续歼灭其余两个团，基本上解决六十八师。邮城战役结束后休整十天左右向西进击，用各个击破方法将孙震以刘汝明两集团大部歼灭，使邱胡陷于孤立，然后解决邱胡。（二）我乘谭军于薄水作战胜利后发起游南作战，已解决二十八师之一九二旅，现正向七十四师攻击中","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"bd4500dda8"},{"id":"4da6f00f3e","type":"paragraph","text":"军委","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"bd4500dda8"},{"id":"b41a318641","type":"paragraph","text":"成东i]这是毛泽东为中共中央军委起草的给署党鲁豫野战军司今员刘伯承和政治委员邓小平的电报。121刘汝明，当时任国民党军第四缓靖区司令官[3]孙震，当时任国民党军第五缓靖区司令官14]邱，指邱清泉，当时任国民党军第五军军长。胡，指胡造，当时任国民党军整编第十一师师长。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"bd4500dda8"},{"id":"ef15c13879","type":"paragraph","text":"栗谭，指票裕、谭震林，当时分别任华中野战军司令员和政治委员。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"bd4500dda8"}],"page":{"id":"e82ea402a9","publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"bd4500dda8","start":249,"end":249}}}},"__N_SSG":true}